OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FMikel Arteta hailed his "incredible"
OL,7,Fplayers for "making history" after
OL,8,FArsenal secured their place in the
OL,9,FChampions League final with a 1-0 win
OL,10,Fagainst Atletico Madrid at the
OL,11,FEmirates Stadium.
OL,13,FBukayo Saka delivered the decisive
OL,14,Fgoal on the stroke of half-time to
OL,15,Ffire the Gunners to a 2-1 aggregate
OL,16,Fsemi-final triumph. They will face
OL,17,Feither Bayern Munich or Paris St
OL,18,FGermain in Budapest on May 30.
OL,26,@nD@YOUnD@dO]oD@MOUoD@\O]
