OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FFollowing Manchester City's 3-3 draw
OL,7,Fat Everton on Monday ` which puts the
OL,8,FPremier League title race in Arsenal's
OL,9,Fhands ` and their triumph over Diego
OL,10,FSimeone's side here just 24 hours
OL,11,Flater, Arteta's men are now only four
OL,12,Fmatches away from completing a
OL,13,Fmomentous double and securing the
OL,14,Fgreatest campaign in the club's 140-
OL,15,Fyear history.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
