CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FArsenal have never won Europe's
OL,7,Fgrandest tournament, and Arteta said:
OL,8,F"It was an incredible night. We made
OL,9,Fhistory again together and I cannot be
OL,10,Fhappier and prouder for everybody
OL,11,Fthat's involved in this football club.
OL,13,F"The supporters were with us for every
OL,14,Fball. They made it special and unique,
OL,15,Fand I have never felt it like that in
OL,16,Fthis stadium.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
