FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,F"We knew how much it meant to
OL,7,Feverybody, we put everything on the
OL,8,Fline, the boys did an incredible job
OL,9,Fand after 20 years, and the second
OL,10,Ftime in our history, we are back in
OL,11,Fthe Champions League final."
OL,13,FArsenal will arrive for the showpiece
OL,14,Fas the sole unbeaten team in this
OL,15,Fseason's competition following a
OL,16,Fremarkable record of 11 wins and three
OL,17,Fdraws. Indeed, their streak of 14
OL,18,Fmatches without defeat is a new
OL,19,FChampions League record for the north
OL,20,FLondon club.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
