SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FBut Arteta's side will next take on
OL,7,FWest Ham at the London Stadium on
OL,8,FSunday, prior to a home match against
OL,9,FBurnley and an away clash at Crystal
OL,10,FPalace. Three wins will be enough for
OL,11,FArsenal to secure their first Premier
OL,12,FLeague title in 22 years before they
OL,13,Fhead to Hungary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
