CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FAnd Arteta added: "It's great.
OL,7,FEverybody can feel a shift in energy,
OL,8,Fin belief, in everything. Let's use it
OL,9,Fin the right way and understand that
OL,10,Fthe margins and the difficulty of what
OL,11,Fwe are trying to achieve are huge, but
OL,12,Fthat we have the ability and the
OL,13,Fconviction to do it.
OL,26,@nD@SOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
