PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,F"I'm really going to enjoy it tonight,
OL,7,Feverybody's enjoying this moment now.
OL,8,FBut tomorrow we have to start to
OL,9,Fprepare for Sunday. We have an
OL,10,Fincredible game against West Ham, a
OL,11,Freally tough one, and we're going to
OL,12,Fhave four days to do that. Let's enjoy
OL,13,Fthe moment but tomorrow let's start to
OL,14,Flive in the present."
OL,16,FAtleti head coach Simeone appeared to
OL,17,Fshove Arsenal sporting director Andrea
OL,18,FBerta on the touchline in the
OL,19,Fconcluding moments of the game.
OL,20,FHowever, he was magnanimous in defeat.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
