PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1778054737
OL,3,CMikel Arteta thrilled as Arsenal 'make
OL,4,Chistory together' in Champions League
OL,6,FSimeone said: "If we got knocked out
OL,7,Fit is because our opponents deserved
OL,8,Fto get through. I don't want to make
OL,9,Fexcuses.
OL,11,F"Mikel Arteta has done an incredible
OL,12,Fjob at Arsenal. He has been trying to
OL,13,Fget to this point for a long time, to
OL,14,Fwin the Premier League and the
OL,15,FChampions League.
OL,17,F"They have incredible financial power,
OL,18,Fand that is linked to what they are
OL,19,Fdoing, but I am pleased for them
OL,20,Fbecause they deserve it."
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
